    "name": "Highlight Webhooks API",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "description": {
      "content": "Outbound webhook callbacks fired when a Highlight alert (Error, Session, User, Log, Trace, or Metric monitor) matches. Customers register a webhook destination URL on an alert; Highlight POSTs the alert payload as JSON. This is the receiver-side contract — the customer's HTTP endpoint must implement `POST /` and acknowledge with `2xx`.\n\n\nContact Support:\n Name: Highlight Support",
      "type": "text/plain"
    }
  }
